<h1>Zombie Rush</h1>
This is my final solo project, developed during my third year at University.
It is a top-down shooter featuring state machines, upgrade trees, an inventory system, saving and loading progress, and more. 
Unfortunately, I no longer have access to the repository since leaving university, but I did create a blog which details the development process.
